<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/790607-while-i-m-waiting-to-begin-a-novel">While I&#39;m waiting to begin a novel recommended to me by a dear friend, is it okay to re-read a couple of oldies from our sagging bookshelves? Just finished re-reading &quot;Atlas Shrugged&quot; for the 1,000th time, and picked up &quot;Magnificent Obsession,&quot; for the bazillionth. Who knows, I may segue into &quot;The Great Gatsby&quot; before returning to the 21st Century!</a>
</div>
