<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/57341765-the-deep-places"><img alt="The Deep Places: A Memoir of Illness and Discovery" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1631506792l/57341765._SX98_.jpg" />
